Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸不合啊  好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去准备新的
